OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'kind' dad killed
OL,4,Cby HGV on motorway
OL,6,FThe family of a dad-of-two who died
OL,7,Fafter being hit by a HGV on the M57
OL,8,Fmotorway say he was "funny, kind and
OL,9,Fhad a huge heart" and they will "miss
OL,10,Fhim forever".
OL,12,FSteven Moglione, 48, died on the M57
OL,13,Fon Merseyside on on Saturday 20 April.
OL,15,FEmergency services were contacted just
OL,16,Fbefore 3.45am following reports that a
OL,17,Fman had been involved in a collision
OL,18,Fwith a HGV on the Northbound side of
OL,19,Fthe motorway between junctions 2 and 3.
