OL,6,FThe driver of the HGV stopped at the
OL,7,Fscene and assisted detectives in
OL,8,Funderstanding the full circumstances
OL,9,Fof what happened.
OL,11,FSteven's family have now issued the
OL,12,Ffollowing statement: "This has come as
OL,13,Fa huge shock to the family who are
OL,14,Fcurrently comforting each other at
OL,15,Fthis extremely hard time.
OL,17,F"Steven will be deeply missed by all
OL,18,Fof his family and friends, he was a
OL,19,Fdevoted husband, father, son, brother
OL,20,F& uncle a true family man.
