OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'kind' dad killed
OL,4,Cby HGV on motorway
OL,6,F"Steven was funny, kind and had a huge
OL,7,Fheart, he was loved by everyone who
OL,8,Fmet him.
OL,10,F"His wife, two children and family
OL,11,Fwill miss him forever but will be
OL,12,Feternally grateful for the love and
OL,13,Ffun times they have shared together".
OL,15,FThe motorway was closed for 15 hours
OL,16,Fafter the crash.
