OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Kurt Timpson, Lead
OL,7,FInvestigating Officer from the
OL,8,FMerseyside Police Serious Collision
OL,9,FInvestigation Unit said: "My thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with Steven's family at this
OL,11,Fsad time.
OL,13,F"They are being supported by specially
OL,14,Ftrained Police Officers. I would ask
OL,15,Fthat they are now allowed the time and
OL,16,Fprivacy to comes to terms with their
OL,17,Floss.
