OL,3,CFamily's tribute to 'kind' dad killed
OL,4,Cby HGV on motorway
OL,6,F"I would like to appeal to anyone who
OL,7,Fwas on the M57 Northbound at the time
OL,8,Fof this collision to please get in
OL,9,Ftouch.
OL,11,F"We know from initial enquiries that
OL,12,Fseveral other vehicles passed through
OL,13,Fthis area just after the collision and
OL,14,Fit is extremely important that we
OL,15,Fspeak with those drivers, even if they
OL,16,Fdid not physically witness the
OL,17,Fcollision.
OL,19,F"The vehicle involved was a DAF Heavy
OL,20,FGoods Vehicle and the collision
OL,21,Fhappened at 3.40am on Saturday morning.
